      "role": "user",
      "content": "honestly i dont even know why i bother trying anymore. it’s just the same thing every single time. i get a job, i mess it up. i try to meet someone, i sabotage it. i try to get my head straight, and then i’m right back at zero. it feels like i’m just running in circles and getting more tired every day. like there's no actual way out of this loop.",
